Unix beard
[[Image:Richard Stallman straining his bowels.jpg|thumb|right|300px|[[Richard Stallman]]'s Unix beard punishing him for using proprietary software]]
[[Image:Ken n dennis.jpg|thumb|Photo of UNIX's creators]]

A '''Unix beard''' is an elder god which has a parasitic relationship with elite users of [[Unix]] or [[Linux]].

Smug, fat, old, unix-adoring fucks who couldn't escape the gravity their social class.

Contrary to the belief of many, [[Rob Levin]] is no unix beard.

[[Richard Stallman]] on the other hand, is basically their pope.

